item.title: 1. Quicktour
item.description: Hallo ig bis! Lab 1: Quicktour Hugo In this lab we will introduce the core concepts of Hugo. What is Hugo? Hugo is a fast and modern static site generator written in Go, and designed to make website creation fun again. Hugo is a general-purpose website framework. Technically speaking, Hugo is a static site generator. Unlike systems that dynamically build a page with each visitor request, Hugo builds pages when you create or update your content.
